data.text:
What is the meaning of the name Maxime?

The name Maxime is primarily a male name of French origin that means Greatest.

French form of the name Maximilian.

Famous people with the name include Maxime Bernier, former Canadian Minister of Foreign Affairs. Maxime Bôcher, American mathematician. Maxime Du Camp, French writer and photographer. Maxime Chaya, Lebanese explorer. Maxime Cressy, American tennis player. Maxime Dupé, French footballer.
